Ensure you have Google Test installed and correctly linked to your project. The specific compilation steps depend on your development environment and how you've set up Google Test.

A generic g++ compilation command might look like this, assuming gtest is installed in a common library path:

```sh
g++ -o factorial_test factorial_test.cpp -lgtest -lgtest_main -pthread
```

And to execute the tests:

```sh
./factorial_test
```

